    <h2>1. Background</h2>
    <p>Academy is a part of the consulting company Academic Work with a concept to fulfil the competence needs of the market, using a concept of accelerated learning. One of those programs teaches programming with the object-oriented language C# on the .NET Framework during a 12-week time span. The program has the goal that the participants will become IT-consultants [1]. The course ends with a 2 week final project, where the knowledge obtained during the course is applied.</p>

